MAGIC_FENCE_ID

public static final String MAGIC_FENCE_ID
Larger region to be monitored that when exited, triggers the app to get a new set of fence data from ExactTarget. An Android app can only monitor so many fences at a time, so this special fence ensures we only monitor fences that are in the user's regional location.

toGeofence

public com.google.android.gms.location.Geofence toGeofence()
Used internally by ExactTarget and not to be called by developers. Converts a Region object into a Geofence object that Android can monitor. Digs into the Region's messages to see whether they are entry/exit and ensures the Geofence is set up for proper triggering and timeouts.
